  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Summon 3 biotic orbs that float around you, fueling your biotic energies. As an action, you may expend an orb and make a ranged spell attack on a creature within 40m. On a hit, deal force damage equal to 2d10 + your spellcasting ability modifier.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>As an action, you may expend 3 orbs to cast a spell using your highest available spell slot. Casting a spell in this way does not consume the spell slot.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>At Higher Levels: When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the number of orbs increases by 2 for each slot level above the 2nd.</p>",
